42029,2230,'_clean_suggest_list_6_item','field_629dbd3526800'),(42030,2230,'clean_suggest_list','7'),(42031,2230,'_clean_suggest_list','field_629dbd35267ff'),(42032,2230,'clean_suggest',''),(42033,2230,'_clean_suggest','field_629dbd35267fd'),(42034,2230,'clean_video_0_title','日常清洁'),(42035,2230,'_clean_video_0_title','field_629dbd3526806'),(42036,2230,'clean_video_0_content_description','较小面积或机器无法使用的区域，我们可采用手动清洁的方式。日常的简单清洁我们只需使用吸尘器、拖把、软毛刷、温水进行清洁即可。清洁频率可根据环境情况而定，顽固脏污需采取特殊清洁剂处理，请参考（污渍处理）。'),(42037,2230,'_clean_video_0_content_description','field_629dbd3526808'),(42038,2230,'clean_video_0_content_list',''),(42039,2230,'_clean_video_0_content_list','field_629dbd3526809'),(42040,2230,'clean_video_0_content',''),(42041,2230,'_clean_video_0_content','field_629dbd3526807'),(42042,2230,'clean_video_0_video_0_image','50'),(42043,2230,'_clean_video_0_video_0_image','field_629dbd352680c'),(42044,2230,'clean_video_0_video_0_url','https://youtu.be/8D2fVLGw2SU'),(42045,2230,'_clean_video_0_video_0_url','field_629dbd352680d'),(42046,2230,'clean_video_0_video_1_image','55'),(42047,2230,'_clean_video_0_video_1_image','field_629dbd352680c'),(42048,2230,'clean_video_0_video_1_url','https://youtu.be/dQw4w9WgXcQ'),(42049,2230,'_clean_video_0_video_1_url','field_629dbd352680d'),(42050,2230,'clean_video_0_video','2'),(42051,2230,'_clean_video_0_video','field_629dbd352680b'),(42052,2230,'clean_video_1_title','深度清洁'),(42053,2230,'_clean_video_1_title','field_629dbd3526806'),(42054,2230,'clean_video_1_content_description','除日常的简单清洁外，深度清洁可以帮助地板恢复到更好状态。较小面积区域或无法使用机器的区域，可采取手动深度清洁的方式，大面积区域可以采用机器清洁：'),(42055,2230,'_clean_video_1_content_description','field_629dbd3526808'),(42056,2230,'clean_video_1_content_list_0_item','先使用吸尘器清除表面灰尘后，去除地板上各种顽固污渍，请参考（污渍处理）'),(42057,2230,'_clean_video_1_content_list_0_item','field_629dbd352680a'),(42058,2230,'clean_video_1_content_list_1_item','再使用软毛刷或者洗地机、温水和少量多功能清洁剂（pH8-11）对地面进行刷洗，刷洗方向尽量沿着地板纵向纹理进行'),(42059,2230,'_clean_video_1_content_list_1_item','field_629dbd352